comments.text:
Here's a poem based on the all time romantic Saga The Notebook
Enjoy

What is Love?
Love is something real he
As they truly feel. 
When two people kiss
They are in eternal bliss.
 Even though it was an awful separation
For Allie it was a great desperation.  
As she moved away
Noah’s memories seemed to stay. 
With the realities of life and war
Their love was one they could afford.  
Seven years after they met
The stage was set.
Again they fell into the bond they once shared
As they knew it to be there
The man she chose. 
Was to be her only rose.  
To Noah she ran
Her one and only biggest fan.
As an old man reading to his wife
To help her remember about her life. 
As there moment of romance was brief
As it turned right back to grief. 
In her room they die together
As they will live on forever.  
Is it true love you want to find?
It is that someone who’s always on your mind.  
Inspired by the movie the Notebook
By Bryanna Saliba

Dedicated: to all lovers young and old
